flattened_params = {'batches_count': 50, 'epochs': 4000, 'k': 200, 'eta': 
    15, 'loss': 'nll', ('loss_params', 'margin'): 2, 'regularizer': 'LP', (

    'optimizer': 'adam', ('optimizer_params', 'lr'): 0.001, 'verbose': 
    False, 'model_name': 'ComplEx'}

expected = {'batches_count': 50, 'epochs': 4000, 'k': 200, 'eta': 15,
    'loss': 'nll', 'loss_params': {'margin': 2}, 'regularizer': 'LP',
    'regularizer_params': {'p': 1, 'lambda': 1e-05}, 'optimizer': 'adam',
    'optimizer_params': {'lr': 0.001}, 'verbose': False, 'model_name':
    'ComplEx'}
assert params == expected
